@Node "AX_TODO" "IntuiNews.guide/AX_TODO"
@Next "AX_REPORTS"
@Prev "AX_CREDITS"
@Toc "Main"

What is to do
=============

   We are working on IntuiNews for about a year and it got quite large
meanwhile.  But because our time is limited we were not able to realize
all desirable features. Here are some of our future plans:

   @{b}*@{ub} ARexx port support (Suggestions are welcome)

   @{b}*@{ub} User configurable menus for external programs

   @{b}*@{ub} Mail aliases (user groups)

   There is absolutely NO guarantee that these features will ever be
implemented.  So don't be disappointed, if they aren't in the next
version.


@EndNode

